Package com.example.demo.strategy.firing

package com.example.demo.strategy.firing
  • Class
    Description
    BossFiringStrategy
    The BossFiringStrategy class implements the FiringStrategy interface and defines the firing behavior for a boss character.
    EnemyFiringStrategy
    The EnemyFiringStrategy class implements the FiringStrategy interface and defines the firing behavior for enemy planes.
    FiringStrategy
    The FiringStrategy interface defines the contract for different firing strategies that can be implemented for a FighterPlane.
    MultiPhaseBossFiringStrategy
    The MultiPhaseBossFiringStrategy class implements the FiringStrategy interface and defines the firing behavior for a multi-phase boss in a game.
    UserFiringStrategy
    The UserFiringStrategy class implements the FiringStrategy interface and defines the firing behavior for user planes.
